            <div type="edition" subtype="transcription" ana="b1" xml:lang="arc">
   <p>הדה נפשׁה דמוסיס בר מרסה דמית בשׁתה<lb/>תליתה דשׁבואה בירח כסלו בעסרין
                        ושׁבעה<lb/>יומינ ביה היא שׁנת רצ שׁנין<lb/>
                  <space extent="unknown" unit="character"/>לחרבן בית מקדשׁה. <space extent="unknown" unit="character"/></p>
                <p><foreign xml:lang="grc">Μνημῖον</foreign> <foreign xml:lang="grc">Μουσῖ</foreign>
                    <lb/><foreign xml:lang="grc">Μάρσου</foreign>, <foreign xml:lang="grc">γενη<unclear>θ</unclear>έντος</foreign>
                    <lb/><foreign xml:lang="grc">ἔτους</foreign> <num value="235" xml:lang="grc">σλε</num>, 
                    <foreign xml:lang="grc"><unclear>ἀπο</unclear>θανόν<lb break="no"/>τος</foreign>
                    <foreign xml:lang="grc"><expan><abbr>ἔτ</abbr><ex>ους</ex></expan></foreign>
                        <num value="253">σνγ</num>.
                    <lb/><foreign xml:lang="grc">Ε<unclear>ὑ</unclear>μοιρίτω</foreign>.
                </p>
            </div>
          
            <div type="translation" ana="b1">
                
                    <p>This is the tombstone of Mousis, son of Marsha, who died in the year three of
                        the seven-year cycle, in the month of Kislev, on the twenty seventh day of
                        it, which is th eyear 290 years of the destruction of the Sanctuary.</p>
                
                
                    <p>Monument of Mousi(s), son of Marsos, who was born in (the) year 235 (and)
                        died in (the) year 253. May his lot be good.</p>
                
            </div>
